c: 19
v: 12
t: "O Yahya\", he was told, \"take the Book AL-Tawrah (the Torah) adhere to all that We have imparted to you and observe the code of discipline and body of regulations and hold them in esteem and hold to your promise and pay attention. Regard to it and be mindful of Our commandments\", and We imbued him with wisdom in his childhood"